'''可颂甜甜圈'''（{{lang-en|cronut}}），别称'''牛角甜甜圈'''，是[[美国|美国]][[纽约|纽约]]糕点厨师Dominique Ansel发明的[[糕点|糕点]]。[[时代杂志|时代杂志]]把它称为2013年25个最佳发明之一。<ref>[http://techland.time.com/2013/11/14/the-25-best-inventions-of-the-year-2013/slide/the-cronut/ {{lang|en|The Cronut}}] {{Wayback|url=http://techland.time.com/2013/11/14/the-25-best-inventions-of-the-year-2013/slide/the-cronut/ |date=20160413053311 }}. TIME.</ref>

Cronut这个名称是[[混成詞|混成词]]，源自于crossaint（[[牛角面包|牛角面包]]）和donut（[[甜甜圈|甜甜圈]]）。<ref>[http://www.bostonglobe.com/ideas/2013/06/08/why-love-cronuts/8CDRreTmBcE7ArxY2pg0BN/story.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/ideas/2013/06/08/why-love-cronuts/8CDRreTmBcE7ArxY2pg0BN/story.html |date=20210214004005 }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/ideas/2013/06/08/why-love-cronuts/8CDRreTmBcE7ArxY2pg0BN/story.html |date=20210214004005 }} {{lang|en|Why we love 'cronuts': The devilish pull of the food portmanteau}}]. Boston Globe.</ref>

